t sjv private school\nI will like to tell some line for this school\n\"Jab shikshak kaamchor honge to bharat kese aage badhega tere jese sab bangaye to har bacha piche hirahega\nJab bhi pase ki bhuk jagti he inko bacchon ki yaad aati he na jane ham jeso ko kitna inhone luta he par fir bhi kya kare name hi school ka kuch asa he\nHar saal bache idhar aake rote he\nMano jase apne maa baap ko khote he\nKab ya daldal khatam hoga ab intezaar hi nhi hota h\nMe har din  khuda se kehta hu ya kya hogai he meri zindagi\nKhuda bhi awaj dete he ab tamanh hogi poori meri\nHar din yeh pal mujhe yad rahega ki mane kyu apna 2 saal idhar barbad karvaya\nMano jase apne hath ko talwar se katwaya\n\nThank you",
